# Normalize line endings on commit: text files are stored with LF in the repo
# and checked out with LF on all platforms. This keeps `biome format`
# deterministic across contributors and lets CI enforce formatting without
# CRLF/LF drift producing spurious diffs.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Treat common binary assets as binary so git never applies EOL conversion.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.webp binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.ttf binary
*.eot binary
*.pdf binary
*.zip binary
